1) Title:

Search for bookings.

Description:

As a page visitor, i need the ability to search all available bookings.

Acceptance criteria:

A site visitor is able to open the site and start a search query on all free rooms

and a date, information about which he can enter in a separate field. 

He can also leave any of the fields empty, in this case he will get all of available variants.

