3) Title:

Change status from «Guest» to «User»

As a guest, i’d like to create an account and login into it upon completing my guest booking.

Acceptance criteria:

Upon confirming a guest booking, system asks user whether he wants to register itself, or not.

If a user answers positively, transfer it to the separate registration page.

If not, do nothing.


